Summary: Biochemical reaction from naproxen to naproxen glucuronide. This interaction can be catalyzed by UGT1A9, UGT2B7 or UGT1A6.
Biochemical reaction from naproxen to desmethylnaproxen. This interaction can be catalyzed by CYP2C9 or CYP1A2.
Biochemical reaction from desmethylnaproxen to desmethylnaproxen acyl glucuronide. This interaction can be catalyzed by UGT1A6, UGT1A3, UGT1A1, UGT1A9 or UGT2B7.
Biochemical reaction from desmethylnaproxen to desmethylnaproxen glucuronide. This interaction can be catalyzed by UGT1A1 or UGT1A9.
